name: Sweet Omelette Recipe | Gulzar Hussain | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Sweet Omelette Recipe: Eggs 3-4 Sugar 2 tbsp Raisins ½ cup Finely Chopped Cashew Nuts ½ cup Finely Chopped Almonds ½ cup Mixture of 4 Nuts 3-4 tbsp Oil 3-4 tbsp
instructions: Take a mixing bowl add 3-4 eggs beat it well add 2 tbsp of sugar Add 1/2 cup of raisin, ½ cup of finely chopped cashew nuts, ½ cup of finely chopped almonds 3-4 tbsp of Mixture of 4 Nuts mix it well Take a fry pan add 3-4 tbsp of cooking oil Heat the oil spread the egg on fry pan fry on the both of the sides When the omelet is ready take it out in a serving platter and serve it.
